04ED            254   ROW1 EQU P1.2
04ED            255   ROW2 EQU P1.4
04ED            256   ROW3 EQU P1.6
04ED            257   ROW4 EQU P2.0
04ED            258   
04ED            259   COL1 EQU P2.2
04ED            260   COL2 EQU P2.4
04ED            261   COL3 EQU P2.6
04ED            262   COL4 EQU P3.0
